## 🚀 Day 2: To-Do List App – Core Functionality & UI

### ✅ What I did today:
- Created UI layout using HTML & CSS
- Implemented **task creation dynamically** using JavaScript
- Styled task items with glowing effect (Neon + Gradient)
- Added:
  - ✅ Add Task
  - 🗑️ Delete Task
  - ☑️ Mark as Complete
  - 🧭 Filter Tabs → All / Completed / Pending
- Used `setAttribute()` and DOM manipulation for structure control
- Added **scroll behavior** for overflow handling
- Customized **scrollbar** using WebKit for theme consistency

### 🎯 What’s next:
- [ ] Save tasks in `localStorage`
- [ ] Add voice input with Web Speech API
- [ ] Add date/time of task creation
- [ ] Animate checkbox/toggle transitions

